law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 188, sec. 69. effective December 1, 1972. -- Amended 1970 Ky. Acts ch. 23, sec. 3, effective June 18, 1970. -- Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 137, sec. 3, effective June 19, 1952. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 242, sec. 14, effective March 23, 1946.
